HEADWORD: Clambake
<hw>Clam"bake</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The backing or
steaming of clams on heated stones, between layers of seaweed; hence, a
picnic party, gathered on such an occasion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

